  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hollowglass</strong> - Atmospheric first-person horror about the last minutes of survival in the desert, despite all its dangers.<br><br>Try to survive at least one more moment. The source of water is already very close, do not be <strong>afraid of jackals</strong>, do not be <strong>afraid of vultures</strong>, do not be <strong>afraid of pain</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547580/extras/ae368b8fa97cb25be4eae5252a0b9921.poster.avif?t=1748475401\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547580/extras/ae368b8fa97cb25be4eae5252a0b9921.webm?t=1748475401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547580/extras/ae368b8fa97cb25be4eae5252a0b9921.mp4?t=1748475401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not <strong>listen to the voice</strong>, do not <strong>slow down</strong>, hold on to the stick as if it were the last thing left of you. The source of water is already very close, do not be <strong>afraid of death</strong>, do not be <strong>afraid of snakes</strong>, do not be <strong>afraid of the desert</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547580/extras/4cf3158199c9039e33ecca90e9bd2b7b.poster.avif?t=1748475401\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547580/extras/4cf3158199c9039e33ecca90e9bd2b7b.webm?t=1748475401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547580/extras/4cf3158199c9039e33ecca90e9bd2b7b.mp4?t=1748475401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not <strong>listen to yourself</strong>, you know the direction, do not stumble and keep moving even when there is nothing left to move with. The source of water is already very close, do not be <strong>afraid of emptiness</strong>, do not be <strong>afraid of it</strong>, do not be <strong>afraid</strong>...<br><br>Features: <br>- Graphics stylized as PS1 <br>- Various dangers <br>- Well-developed artificial intelligence of jackals</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hollowglass</strong> - Atmospheric first-person horror about the last minutes of survival in the desert, despite all its dangers.<br><br>Try to survive at least one more moment. The source of water is already very close, do not be <strong>afraid of jackals</strong>, do not be <strong>afraid of vultures</strong>, do not be <strong>afraid of pain</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547580/extras/ae368b8fa97cb25be4eae5252a0b9921.poster.avif?t=1748475401\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547580/extras/ae368b8fa97cb25be4eae5252a0b9921.webm?t=1748475401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547580/extras/ae368b8fa97cb25be4eae5252a0b9921.mp4?t=1748475401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not <strong>listen to the voice</strong>, do not <strong>slow down</strong>, hold on to the stick as if it were the last thing left of you. The source of water is already very close, do not be <strong>afraid of death</strong>, do not be <strong>afraid of snakes</strong>, do not be <strong>afraid of the desert</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547580/extras/4cf3158199c9039e33ecca90e9bd2b7b.poster.avif?t=1748475401\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547580/extras/4cf3158199c9039e33ecca90e9bd2b7b.webm?t=1748475401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547580/extras/4cf3158199c9039e33ecca90e9bd2b7b.mp4?t=1748475401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not <strong>listen to yourself</strong>, you know the direction, do not stumble and keep moving even when there is nothing left to move with. The source of water is already very close, do not be <strong>afraid of emptiness</strong>, do not be <strong>afraid of it</strong>, do not be <strong>afraid</strong>...<br><br>Features: <br>- Graphics stylized as PS1 <br>- Various dangers <br>- Well-developed artificial intelligence of jackals</p>",
